(154, '2022-03-13 12:42:40', 'others', 'Traffic Rules Violence', 'Malik Umar', '', '', 'malikumar9991@gmail.com', '', '', 'CTO', 'Subject:  Traffic Rules Violence\r\n\r\nRespected Sir, \r\n\r\nI hope you are doing well, I am just letting you know, in our city Jaranwala, people are not following the traffic one-way rule on these roads. I have attached a picture with this application and highlighted the roads in the picture, I do not know our regional traffic officer is aware of this situation or not  Day by day I see lots of people drive in opposite directions, and this is the main cause of accidents. No one is on duty on this road, Why we are waiting for the big accident? You should be taking action on it.  \r\nRoad No 1: Near Bismillah Petrol Pum\r\nRoad No 2. Near Defence View Colony\r\n\r\nPlease take action as soon as possible, your action will save our life. \r\nBeing a Good Citizen Of Pakistan, \r\n\r\n\r\nThanks & Regards,\r\n\r\nTehsil Jaranwala, Faisalabad', 'Your complaint has been forwarded to Complaint Cell Branch City Traffic Police Faisalabad for further action.', '130322-CTO-30396'),
