(1412, 'Renewal License', '<div><span class=\"style1\" style=\"font-weight: bold; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; line-height: normal; text-align: justify;\"><br></span></div><span class=\"style1\" style=\"font-weight: bold; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; line-height: normal; text-align: justify;\">THE FOLLOWING DOCUMENTS ARE REQUIRED FOR RENEWAL OF LICENSE :</span><br style=\"color: rgb(17, 104, 171); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; text-align: justify;\"><br style=\"color: rgb(17, 104, 171); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(17, 104, 171); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; line-height: normal; text-align: justify;\">1. Required application form</span><br style=\"color: rgb(17, 104, 171); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; text-align: justify;\"><br style=\"color: rgb(17, 104, 171); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(17, 104, 171); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; line-height: normal; text-align: justify;\">2. Two (02) passport size photo graph&nbsp;</span><br style=\"color: rgb(17, 104, 171); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; text-align: justify;\"><br style=\"color: rgb(17, 104, 171); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(17, 104, 171); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; line-height: normal; text-align: justify;\">3. A copy of C.N.I.C</span><br style=\"color: rgb(17, 104, 171); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12p